description: The accused faces 79 charges of causing or inciting children under 16 to engage in sexual activity.
title: Newry man Alexander McCartney faces 193 'catfishing' charges
title_page: Newry man Alexander McCartney faces 193 'catfishing' charges - BBC News
maintext: It is the police case that the schoolgirl sent a naked picture of herself to the defendant who is then alleged to have blackmailed her that "if she didn't do what was asked her image would be uploaded to the internet".
